{"serial": "18007", "department_serial": 13, "code": "IL4406", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Project in Humanities: Festival, Archive and production", "ch": "人文應用專題：電影策展"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Wafa Ghermani"], "ch": ["倪娃法"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["6", "7", "8"]}, "loc": {"building": "C2", "room": "104"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "文學院學士班", "en": "Interdisciplinary Program of Liberal Arts"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "英語", "en": "English"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 20, "selected": 0, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "1.透過個案研究讓學生認知電影的物質性以及保存與修復的挑戰。\n2.學生能發揮策展技能企劃節目，包括：理念、版權歸屬與電影介紹。\n3.學生能增進對於電影以及活動節目的研究技能。", "en": "1.Discover the different aspects of film preservation.\n2 Understand the materiality of film, the challenges of conservation and restoration of films. \n2.Develop skills in event organization to create a film program : conception, research of the right holder, the technical questions.\n3.Developing research skills on films"}, "outline": {"ch": "本課程主要為實作練習，包含工作坊（小組討論、電影介紹以及電影手冊撰寫等）、參觀資料館、博物館等場所，並邀請專業人士交流。\n第一週    課程介紹：電影資料館與記憶\n第二週    電影資料館歷史。\n第三週     電影策展\n第四週    參觀電影蒐藏家博物館 (日期待確認）\n第五週    從底片到數位檔案\n第六週    參觀國家電影及視聽文化中心 (日期待確認）\n第七週    兒童節補假1日\n第八週    修復的倫理\n第九週    參觀國家電影及視聽文化中心片庫 (日期待確認）\n第十週     策展電影內容介紹\n第十一週  參觀現代電影公司 (日期待確認）\n第十二週 修復電影的發展\n第十三週  影展之週\n第十四週  應檔案的使用\n第十五週  電影資料館的串流電影平台\n第十六週  期末呈現", "en": "The course will be mainly practical. With on site workshops ( work in group, , presenting a film, writing film introduction), visits to archives, museum and other places, meeting professionals.\nWeek 1 ：Course introduction : Film Archive and memory\nWeek 2  : History of Film archives\nWeek 3:   Curating film\nWeek 4     Visit to Film Collectors Museum （date to be confirmed)\nWeek 5   From print to digital files\nWeek 6 Visit to the TFAI (1) （date to be confirmed)\nWeek 7 Leave Adjustment for Children‘s Day NO CLASS\nWeek 8  Ethics of restoration\nWeek 9 Visit to the TFAI (2) /film vault（date to be confirmed)\nWeek 10 Evolution of restoration\nWeek 11 Visit to Modern Cinema Lab （date to be confirmed)\nWeek 12 Festival films introduction preparation\nWeek 13 Festival Week\nWeek 14 Using archival films\nWeek 15  Film platforms\nWeek 16 Final presentation"}, "textbook": {"ch": "無", "en": "無"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "0", "en": "0"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "20％ 出席, 40％ 影展 30％ 期末報告", "en": "20％ attendance, 40％ Festival event 40％ final presentation"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "待定", "en": "待定"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "free reading", "en": "Free reading"}, "domain": {"ch": "影像", "en": "影像"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "人文實踐", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "批判思考", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評"]}, {"competencies": "多元敘事", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評"]}, {"competencies": "跨域學習", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評"]}, {"competencies": "組織合作", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "人文實踐", "rating": "(4)High", "assesments": ["Assignments", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "批判思考", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Research Report(printed on paper)", "Practices/Experiments", "Attendance/Performance", "Self Assessment/ Peer Assessment"]}, {"competencies": "多元敘事", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Assignments", 